> **Goal:** Extend the existing A2A module into the CoAgent Protocol (CAP) — A2A + consent engine + data minimization + interaction receipts.

### 4.1 CAP Architecture on Existing A2A

```
CURRENT A2A:
  A2AAdapter dispatches 3 JSON-RPC methods:
    - propose_governance_session
    - select_governance_consensus  
