    - negotiate_consent        ← NEW: receiver checks permission rules
    - exchange_data            ← NEW: send data with minimization headers
    - acknowledge_receipt      ← NEW: both sides log the interaction
    - revoke_access            ← NEW: user revokes another agent's access
