### 4.6 Interaction Receipts

#### [NEW] `InteractionReceipt.java`

```java
package com.coagent4u.a2a.protocol;

/**
 * After every CAP interaction, both agents log a receipt.
 * This is visible to the user in their Transparency Dashboard.
 */
public record InteractionReceipt(
    String interactionId,
    String fromAgent,
    String toAgent,
    String intent,
    String dataShared,      // What was actually shared (post-minimization)
    SharingLevel level,     // What sharing level was used
    Instant timestamp,
    String outcome          // "completed", "denied", "revoked"
) {}
```

These receipts are written to the `agent_activities` table via the existing monitoring module.

